edges.nl_text:
"Greatest of: last login timestamp from CRM (if available),
     @last_transaction_date, and last profile update timestamp.
     This field anchors the retention policy for the target schema."

"Classify the grouped session as:
     purchaser if any purchase event exists;
     engaged if there is any add_to_cart event;
     browse if there are multiple product_view events;
     otherwise bounce."

